re gauges prosense dpg digital pressure gauges are ideal for industrial and general purpose applications requiring an accurate and reliable device with easy to read digital display these dpg gauges have a digit  x  lcd display and button operation the backlight display turns on when the onoff button is pressed and has a continuous on display option or a timeout option to save battery life the display battery life is  years auto shutoff mode or  weeks if the display is on continuously a rubber boot is included for added gauge protection and the process connection is  npt gauge accuracy is   of full scale with available pressure ranges from    psig to    psig pressure unit selections include psi mho mmhg mbar kpa bar kgcm and mpa prosense dpg digital pressure gauges are priced at  and have a year warranty  continuous flexing industrial cate ethernet cable datamax extreme ethernet cable from quabbin® has a specially designed jacket developed to survive the many industrial hazards that commercial jackets will not the datamax cable jacket is pressure extruded over the cable core locking the conductor pairs in place this type of jacket construction provides very stable electrical performance even when impacted bent or repeatedly flexed these cate flexing cables are available in  awg  or  twisted pairs with color coded high density polyethylene insulation and with unshielded or overall braid and foil shields the frtpe jacket has excellent chemical moisture and flame resistance and exceptional low temperature flexibility the cables are type cmx outdoor  cm and awm style  ul classified starting at  continuous flexing cables are made in the usa and are sold in  to  foot lengths  nitra current to pneumatic ip transducers nitra ncp series electropneumatic transducers convert a  ma current signal i from a plc or other controller to a linear pneumatic output pressure p these nitra ip transducers are rated for installation in nema x ip environments and approved for hazardous locations the ncp series ip transducers are available in output pressure ranges up to  psig for industrial pneumatic and process control applications ncp series transducers can be direct or bracket mounted and have a  npt female conduit connection with wire leads compact ncp series ip transducers can be direct or bracket mounted and have a  npt female conduit connection with wire leads or field wireable din  electrical connector optional pipe and din rail mounting kits are also available nitra ip transducers start at  and have a year warranty  precision limit switches traditional limit switches are limited in terms of accuracy and repeatability these costeffective ultraprecise mechanical limit switches from metrol® have repeatability down to    and even  microns µm depending on the specific model along with their high precision these stainless steel limit switches are also some of the smallest switchessensors available their tiny size allows them to be mounted in extremely tight locations five precision limit switch series are available precision touch with  micron or  micron accuracy high precision touch and tool setter with  micron accuracy ball plunger with  micron accuracy and high temperature rated with  micron accuracy and operating temperatures up to °c the switches are iec ip to ip rated depending on model precision limit switches start at  and have a year warranty  ironhorse® shaft mount gearboxes ironhorse shaft mount gearboxes speed reducers feature shafts and gears manufactured from the highest grade steel case hardened and precision ground to agma standards for long lasting durability the gearbox shafts have reinforced double lip seals to protect against contamination and prevent oil from escaping premium ball and tapered roller bearings provide smooth operation and lower noise extended gear centers ensure tooth contact and provide consistent operation housings are  cast iron to provide industrial grade protection for the life of the unit gearboxes are avail